<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR3b0003-zh-f56a2771" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>孫子兵法</title><editor role="translator">Chen Xi 陈曦</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>孫子兵法</title>Beijing: Zhonghuashuju, 2022</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR3b0003"><title xml:lang="och">孫子</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="zh">Chinese</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2024-05-07T05:01:08.083+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR3b0003-start"><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-07T05:02:34.054+09:00">“孙子说：</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-07T05:02:41.203+09:00">军事学研究</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-07T05:02:48.011+09:00">是国家的大事，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-07T05:02:54.283+09:00">它是关乎百姓死活、</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-07T05:03:01.222+09:00">国家存亡的一个思想领域，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-07T15:28:48.375+09:00">不能不深入考察。”</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>